# 🐳 Tunisian Chatbot (Docker + Ollama)

This project is a chatbot powered by **Ollama (LLaMA 3 8B)** and runs fully inside **Docker**.

It supports interactive terminal chat in Arabic/Tunisian dialect.

---

## 🚀 Run with Docker

### ✅ 1) Start Docker containers

Run the following command to build and start everything:

```bash
docker compose up --build

### ✅ 2) Pull the model inside container
After containers are running, open a new terminal and run:

```bash
docker exec -it ollama ollama pull llama3:8b

### ✅ 3) Run chatbot interactively
Because the app uses input(), you must attach to the container:

```bash
docker attach tunisian-chatbot
